title: Kaspersky Rescue Disk 2018 18.0.11.0 Data 2018.07.01 Inc Usb
description:
Description:

Kaspersky Rescue Disk is a free and secure program to remove viruses from computers
without risk of infection. You can use this program to infect a virus when the system
is infected, because the computer is not disinfected using antivirus software or
malware removal software. For example, like the Kaspesky antivirus tool running
under the operating system.
In this case, eliminating contamination
is more effective because malicious programs are not controlled when the operating
system is loaded.To scan and remove threats from an infected computer without
risk of infecting other files or computers,you can boot from Kaspersky Rescue Disk software
